# API 层

## 路由

- 前缀 `/v1`；DisplayGround 在 `/displayground/`
- Policy 创建：`kind` 默认 `dsl`，仅接受 `dsl`
- 编译：`POST /v1/policies/{id}/compile`、`POST /v1/dsl/compile-preview`、`GET /v1/dsl/schema`

## Handler 模式

```go
if !readJSON(w, r, &in) { return }
writeJSON(w, http.StatusOK, map[string]any{...})
s.audit(ctx, actor(r), "action", "entity_type", id, payload)
```

## DisplayGround

- 静态文件 embed 在 `internal/api/displayground/`
- 修改 UI 时保持纯 HTML/JS，无构建步骤
- 创建策略流程：policy → attach role → compile → published → releases

## Authorize

- 输入：`user` + `request`；不查 DB 解析 principal
- 缓存 key 含 revision；`X-Role-Revision` 不匹配时跳过缓存
